manufacturerProductDescription.media_text: Coolife LIFE IS WHERE YOU TAKE IT Coolife Softside Luggage Set

Peace of mind Built-in TSA-approved combination lock provide an added layer of security for travelers while still allowing airport security personnel to perform necessary checks. They help to prevent theft and unauthorized access to luggage, giving passengers peace of mind when traveling.

Ample room for storage A fully-lined roomy interior with convenient mesh pocket, indulge your cargo in every trip you go on. Versatile and durable Made of a water-resistant Oxford cloth, the tote bag is perfect for flights, work, or spontaneous trips. The shoulder strap offers a hands-free solution to easily transport the bag along the road. Ready to go The tote bag can be easily attached to the extended handle of the luggage by its rear strap. Get rolling Designed for 360° rotation, these wheels make navigating busy airports and bustling streets a breeze, allowing you to focus on enjoying your journey rather than struggling with heavy bags.
Great maneuverability Travel in a relaxed and effortless fasion with our luggage. Its light-weight, ergonomic telescopic handle and smooth spinner wheels make it a breeze to maneuver.

Solid companion Made of 1680D Oxford fabric, the luggage enjoys great durability with a more causal or sporty style, making it a right choice for everyone to go with. Corner protector No matter how turbulent the journey, the corner protector shields your luggage corners from dents, scratches, and other forms of damage. Reinforced grip handles It allows travelers to comfortably carry their luggage by hand, providing convenience and ease during their journeys.
Take it easy Convenient dual front pockets allow you to access your boarding pass, laptop, tablet or other thing you need easily. Always be ready and efficient on the road.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on September 21, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Nice set for the money
reviews.reviewText: For across the board road travel, this works well. Don’t know about air travel and their rough handling of your bags.Nice thick and durable outside material that is attractive. Inside is basic but easy to use when packing with cubes. The 2 tie downs keep you organized and in place.The only thing that could improve performance is flat fabric handles to grab on all sides. But, as designed, certainly ok.The stacking is great but you definitely lose real estate inside as you step down in sizes.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 25, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars I love this luggage set!
reviews.reviewText: I haven't travelled since before COVID and realized that my old luggage was OLD. I am so glad I found this set. Besides having so many pieces, the blue is a beautiful color and it is very sturdy and roomy - the luggage travelled very well internationally. I highly recommend this set.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 24, 2024
reviews.reviewText: The media could not be loaded. This luggage is durable, not very heavy, has great every way wheels, retractable handles on each piece.Plus I love the color choice!!They also nest together when not in use.Winning all around.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on April 24, 2022
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars For me it would be that they are extremely lightweight and have lovely wheels that move very easily.
reviews.reviewText: The media could not be loaded. For me it would be that they are extremely lightweight and have lovely wheels that move very easily. I love the carry-on luggage and that it’s lightweight so possibly I can load it or get someone to help me load it in the overhead compartment. I need The small one to carry on the plane with me as I will have to take my CPAP machine and my portable oxygen machine with me and I feel better that The small bag will qualify as a carry-on. Very important my machines don’t get thrown around. I will put in some towels to wrap my machines in my carry-on luggage just for extra protection. I purchased the one made of Very durable materials as the reviews said it was very durable and again I needed light weight luggage for me too manage easily. My favorite color in the whole world is purple and this was an absolute beautiful purple so I am quite pleased with that. The handles are easy retractable and The metal handles that you pull out to roll your luggage around the airport is adjustable with different heights. The handles on the side and the top of the luggage I would assume would really make it very easy for you to place on your bed to pack your clothes in the same thing for unpacking once you get to your destination. I also assume it will make for easy lifting to put above your head on the plane for safe storage .I will have to give you all an update on my experience with my luggage during my vacation. I knew nothing about purchasing luggage and it took a certain size to qualify as a carry-on. I purchased this luggage due to most positive reviews and even if they came a little damaged or damaged during their trip, I understood that the customer said the company which is Coolife read the reviews and reached out to the customer to make sure they could resolve any issues the customer had with their luggage. I will say so far I am very pleased that I decided to choose this brand of luggage. I hope my video presentation of my luggage helps anyone looking for quality luggage at a very reasonable price will be able to make a very informed decision before purchasing another brand.Sincerely, BrandyPurple 💜

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 19, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Cool life luggage
reviews.reviewText: I have traveled for my job, so as you can imagine I go thru a lot of suitcases! I have found the perfect one for me. The wheels are sturdy, the material surprisingly are durable. I also love the color. Recent trip from LAX to PHL and the handcarry luggage held all my essential needs and fit the overhead bin on United perfectly. Love! Love!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on November 19, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Decent luggage set for the price
reviews.reviewText: I wanted to wait until I actually used this luggage for a trip, which I did recently. Here are a couple of things I realized while using this luggage for travel. The suitcases seem pretty sturdy and the spinner wheels work well (hopefully they last a while). I know the dimensions are clear in the product description, but wanted to confirm that only the smallest suitcase is considered a carry-on. I like the size of the medium suitcase but it is too big for a carry-on. Also the smallest suitcase does not have a side handle, which makes it a little difficult to maneuver into the overhead compartment. I also didn't realize when I bought this set that they are not expandable, which would have been a plus. But all in all, a decent set for the price. Hope to use them for a long time!
